Package: minimax-agent
Version: 3.0.46
Section: network
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libnss3 (>= 3.14.3), libx11-6, libx11-xcb1, libxcb1, libxcomposite1, libxdamage1, libxext6, libxfixes3, libxrandr2, libxrender1, libxss1, libxtst6, libglib2.0-0, libgtk-3-0, libnotify4, libnspr4, libdbus-1-3, libdrm2, libgbm1, libasound2
Recommends: systemd, nodejs (>= 18), build-essential
Maintainer: MiniMax
Description: MiniMax Agent Desktop Application
 A powerful AI agent desktop application with chat, tools, and automation capabilities.
 Includes Electron runtime, backend daemon, and all native modules.
 The backend daemon requires Node.js (>= 18), systemd, and build-essential.
 Run setup.sh after installation to complete configuration.
